<exercise>
  <statement>
    <p>
      Find the probability of getting 53 Mondays  in a no leap year.
    </p>
  </statement>
  <solution>
    <p>
      In no year total number of days = 365 days = 52 weaks + 1 day. Hence, the probablity of getting 53 Mondays is 
      <me>
        P(M) = 1/7.
      </me>  
    </p>
  </solution>
</exercise>


